      { type: "paragraph", text: "Is Castle.ai suitable for production use?" },
      { type: "paragraph", text: "Castle.ai is designed as a starting point for real products, not just demos. Whether it's production-ready for your specific use case depends on the modifications you make and the requirements of your application." }
